content: I'm planning my day and wanted to get some help with prioritizing my tasks. I have a few important meetings scheduled for this afternoon, but I also need to make time for a 30-minute walk during my lunch break. Can you suggest a schedule for me to fit everything in? By the way, I'm aiming to be in bed by 11:30 pm at the latest today, so I want to make sure I don't overdo it.
